op: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">txpck/s:每秒钟发送的数据包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">rxbyt/s:每秒钟接收的字节数</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">txbyt/s:每秒钟发送的字节数</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">rxcmp/s:每秒钟接收的压缩数据包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">txcmp/s:每秒钟发送的压缩数据包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">rxmcst/s:每秒钟接收的多播数据包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2）命令：</p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0.88889em; font-size: 0.9em; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border-radius: 4px;\">sar&nbsp;-n&nbsp;NFS&nbsp;-f&nbsp;sa27</pre><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"/static/uploads/image/20190618/1560861050396046.png\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"929\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">IFACE:LAN接口</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">rxerr/s:每秒钟接收的坏数据包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">txerr/s:每秒钟发送的坏数据包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">coll/s:每秒冲突数</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">rxdrop/s:因为缓冲充满，每秒钟丢弃的已接收数据包数</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">txdrop/s:因为缓冲充满，每秒钟丢弃的已发送数据包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">txcarr/s:发送数据包时，每秒载波错误数</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">rxfram/s:每秒接收数据包的帖对齐错误数</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">rxfifo/s:接收的数据包每秒FIFO过速的错误数</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">txfifo/s:发送的数据包每秒FIFO过速的错误数</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '20190618/5540aaf7f43f2d7219ff0612c507c0c3.jpg', '1', '1', null, 'Miss you', '1560861074', '84', '0,80,84,', '2', '0');

